Module worldofzuul
Package worldofzuul.item

Class Item

java.lang.Object
worldofzuul.Sprite
worldofzuul.SpriteAnimation
worldofzuul.item.Item
Direct Known Subclasses:
Fertilizer, Harvester, Irrigator, pHNeutralizers, Plant, Seed
public abstract class Item
extends SpriteAnimation
The type Item. This abstract class determines the Item that can be used by the Player to sold, purchased, turned in using a quest or interacted with upon a GameObject.

    • deplete

      public float deplete()
      Depletes the amount in remaining using consumptionRate. If remaining is smaller than consumptionRate then subtract value until it reaches 0.
      Returns:
      value subtracted from remaining
